OL,3,CXL Bully shook schoolgirl 'like a toy'
OL,5,FA 16-year-old schoolgirl has bravely
OL,6,Frecounted her horror after a suspected
OL,7,FXL Bully dog attacked her in the
OL,8,Fstreet, leaving her needing surgery.
OL,10,FKerris Gledhill, from Norris Green,
OL,11,Fwas walking her miniature dachshund
OL,12,Fwhen the dog reportedly ran towards
OL,13,Fher.
OL,15,F"The dog picked my dog up by its
OL,16,Fharness and shook him," Kerris said,
OL,17,Fdescribing the terrifying moment she
OL,18,Fmanaged to pull Mr Otis behind her and
OL,19,Funder a car.
