OL,3,CXL Bully shook schoolgirl 'like a toy'
OL,5,FShe recalled: "The dog latched onto
OL,6,Fme. I just remember screaming and
OL,7,Fgrabbing hold of my leg... The dog was
OL,8,Fshaking me like I was a toy."
OL,10,FThe 16-year-old was left in crippling
OL,11,Fpain with teeth marks sunk deep into
OL,12,Fher leg. She told her mum, Demi-Lee
OL,13,FGlehill, 32, that she thought she was
OL,14,Fgoing to lose her leg.
OL,16,FDemi-Lee described the phone call from
OL,17,Fher daughter as the "worst" she'd ever
OL,18,Freceived. She rushed to the scene to
OL,19,Ffind Kerris on the floor, "lifeless."
