OL,3,CXL Bully shook schoolgirl 'like a toy'
OL,5,FThe schoolgirl was taken to Aintree
OL,6,FHospital where she later underwent
OL,7,Fsurgery on her leg. Her mum has
OL,8,Fconfirmed that while the injuries are
OL,9,Fhealing, Kerris has been left with
OL,10,F"excess damage" to her thigh and has
OL,11,Flost some feeling.
OL,13,FKerris, who is an animal lover, is now
OL,14,F"traumatised," admitting, "when I'm
OL,15,Fwalking or if I hear a bark, I have a
OL,16,Fpanic attack and my dog is on edge."
